KÃ¶hler S, Sustainable Blockchain Technologies - An Assessment of Social and Environmental Impacts of Blockchain-based Technologies

The supplementary materials to the article include the raw data:

inventory tables: 
2019.csv, 2020.csv, 2021.csv

These are needed to run the scripts contained in this repository, for example if you want to reproduce the results.

The repository includes

BTC_2019-mid-2021.ipynb Python script to reproduce results of the LCA using the brightway2 LCA software. Imports the inventory in, performs LCA calculations and exports LCIA results.

lci_to_bw2.py A little python script to import inventory tables in .csv directly into brightway2.

Please get in touch if you find any mistake or problem in running these scripts.
